ComicInfo.Summary: Five years ago, Aleph was the brilliant underachiever on campus...then she met Miranda Zero, and her life changed. Now she's the focal point of the Global Frequency rescue organization, coordinating crucial data during each operation. That is, until five minutes ago. The Global Frequency HQ has been breached, and Aleph must stand her ground and fight, for her life, and the life of every other agent on the Frequency!
